{"tid":2160754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"工人涉6.26警總水刮襲警兼暴動 控方開審前欲擴犯案範圍 官拒：我要準確性，毫無合理疑點呀！","createTime":"2020-08-17T07:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T02:38:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":333,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"6031ac5347f728fb88cf9117b38732cbd1f8aefd","tid":2160754,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/URXOHQBNJRHSHBDZVD2TRC2L5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FURXOHQBNJRHSHBDZVD2TRC2L5I%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d085446b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FURXOHQBNJRHSHBDZVD2TRC2L5I%2F&h=f9508e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/URXOHQBNJRHSHBDZVD2TRC2L5I/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年 6 月 26 日大批反送中示威者包圍警察總部，當日有便衣警員聲稱欲往警總上班時，遭多名示威者追打，一度手持水刮與示威者對峙，最終由同袍打開捲閘救走。有地盤工被指有份毆打該名便衣警，被控襲擊傷人及暴動等罪，案件今在區域法院開審。控方開案前申請修改暴動範圍，稱要令控罪有更多彈性，惟被法官郭啟安批評「我唔係要彈性，我要準確性呀，毫無合理疑點呀！」控方最終撤回修訂。"},{"pid":"4da912e2d7bd3b8eb6408b2ae73b5f30beb1813f","tid":2160754,"uid":66324,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"DoJ不如修改暴動範圍係全地球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfc84df6b756a16f522ad5c5e755a53ea5662b8","tid":2160754,"uid":135277,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"成班律政狗係咪唔記得咗without reasonable doubt"},{"pid":"0e17c89c7ff5ee9bae808bacbc49e71fcc8e2a28","tid":2160754,"uid":132587,"like":59,"dislike":360,"score":-301,"citedBy":47,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73a8b18c47277bf4edd5cc65f9c4dd80bb1f8616","tid":2160754,"uid":121270,"like":471,"dislike":4,"score":467,"quote":{"pid":"0e17c89c7ff5ee9bae808bacbc49e71fcc8e2a28","tid":2160754,"uid":132587,"like":59,"dislike":360,"score":-301,"citedBy":47,